properties.name: Jaunty McJauntface
properties.description:
Sometimes a bike ride is a heavily planned and highly themed affair, with complex motivations and a meticulously orchestrated route. Highfalutin conceptual conceits are employed to describe it, using carefully crafted prose. One would imagine that puns are somehow be involved, along with Latinate words like "liminal."

And, sometimes, a bike ride is just a relatively short journey or excursion, usually for pleasure.
